 ```
 
-#### `LineChart`
-
-```json
-{"id": "lc1", "component": "LineChart", "title": {"path": "/data/lineTitle"}, "data": {"path": "/data/lineData"}}
-```
+`chartType` enum: `"bar"` | `"line"` | `"donut"` | `"bar_grouped"`
 
